{"article_id":"0MAuUnU4bysdaWfO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Of the show trials in the Soviet Union , it was said ,","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"\" Everything was true , except the facts. \"","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"One could say the same about the show trial","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"Donald Trump is suffering at the hands of a hysterically partisan ruling class .","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Its frenzy over James Comey ' s Senate testimony bears no relationship to reality ;","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"it is simply a reflection of its own ruthless power politics and determination","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"to nail Trump at any cost .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Comey ' s testimony was utterly unpersuasive .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Though presented in high-minded terms ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"it amounted to little more than sour grapes over a sacking , and a wholly justified sacking at that .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Comey ' s directorship was an unmitigated disaster .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"Trump \" lied \" about the reasons for my firing ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"whined Comey .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"No , he didn ' t .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"If Trump said","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"that Comey ' s lousy judgment had caused \" turmoil \" at the FBI ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"that ' s because it did .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"That Comey characterized Trump ' s comments about a demoralized FBI as a \" lie \" should discredit the rest of his testimony .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"It just underscored the straining , self-serving character of his appearance .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"He showed up","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"not to defend an \" independent \" FBI","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"but to justify his own dubious tenure at it .","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"And now it turns out that this great Niehburian conscience of Washington is a self-confirmed leaker .","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"He had a \" friend \" pass a memo to the New York Times in an attempt","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"to parry the president ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"he testified .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"Only a navel-gazing flake like Comey","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"- he left Catholicism for relativistic Methodism -","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"would be deluded enough","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"to think","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"that such admissions enhance his credibility .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"Instead , they just confirm what a self-serving operator he has always been .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"How many other memos did Comey leak to the New York Times ?","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"None of the fawning , drippy senators were going to ask him that .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Comey is clearly responsible for the leaks to the Times after Trump ' s infamous tweets about Obamagate .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"But Comey ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"you understand ,","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"had his scruples :","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"he made sure not to leak the news","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"that Trump himself was not under investigation","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"for colluding with the Russians .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"That was not to get out .","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"Let ' s cut through the nonsense :","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"Comey , not Trump , is the villain in this idiotic saga .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"In all of his heavy-breathing hints and leaks , Comey let people think","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"that the president was under investigation .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"The scandal is not that a guilty president asked the FBI director to treat him as innocent ,","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"but that an innocent president was treated as guilty by an FBI director","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"drunk on his own rectitude .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"One has to laugh at the audacity of an FBI director","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"who violates the confidences of others","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"casting himself as the arbiter of honesty and integrity .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Trump ' s instincts about Comey were absolutely correct .","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"He is the kind of ruling-class creep","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"who takes secret notes on presidents ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"then leaks them to the press ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"all while expecting a pat on the head from the great and good for his \" independence. \"","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"Who elected Comey to such an exalted position ?","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"Comey claimed","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"he understood","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"that he served at the \" pleasure \" of the president .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"But this was BS .","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"He served at his own pleasure ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"and his remarks were designed to pander to the undemocratic opportunism of the Democrats ,","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"under which the least accountable figures","depth":15},{"id":65,"text":"( Supreme Court justices , FBI directors , \" career \" civil servants )","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"are increasingly deified .","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"Trump did not obstruct justice .","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"How could he have ?","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"There was no investigation","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"to obstruct ,","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"as Comey himself pathetically acknowledges .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"The partisan jackasses at CNN had promised","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"that Comey was going to refute Trump ' s claim","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"that Comey told him on three separate occasions","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"that he was not under investigation for collusion .","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"He didn ' t ;","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"he confirmed it .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"So what exactly has Trump lied about ?","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Once again , Trump is more sinned against than sinning .","depth":2},{"id":80,"text":"The media always cast him as the bully ,","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"but","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"when the dust clears ,","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"he more often than not emerges as the victim .","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"Comey sees himself as a white knight ,","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"saving the republic from a vulgarian .","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"But the American people can see","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"that the \" respectability \" of a leaking , vicious , two-faced ruling class doesn ' t add up to much","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"and constitutes a much deeper vulgarity","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"than anything Trump represents .","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"If one can fault Trump for anything in the firing of Comey ,","depth":4},{"id":91,"text":"it is that he didn ' t do it sooner .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":183,"left":170,"right":182,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":113,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":98,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":93,"right":97,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":93,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":97,"left":94,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":4,"right":95,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":95,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":100,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":7,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":99,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":106,"right":110,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":10,"right